{
  "stem": "2966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the head engineer of town of Boryslaw, of our town, came there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a Ukrainian, very nice gentleman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he saw my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he had the privilege of taking a few people out, so he took my father out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my father told him that I am there, and they took-- they released me too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even though the German was squawk-- the officer in charge of the assessment was squawking a little bit, but he did let me go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The other people, of course, were taken out and destroyed-- shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that went on for-- that was already 1943.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after a short while, they closed off, they liquidated the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And at that time they issued [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] a card, which was called an R.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's an identification card, which was called R, for the [GERMAN] industry, which means for the armament industry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And whoever got that R was relocated to another big building that used to be occupied by very poor workers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they had-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] at that place they had horses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They used to be employed in the oil industry, because our roads were very bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that's where they settled the rest of the Jews that were still officially working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And between those people, there was a few that didn't have that R.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was, unfortunately, one of them that didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And at one point, at one action, we were also taken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I'm getting a little bit mixed up with the-- with the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] times of when what happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
